# Dashboard Guidelines

- Keep dashboard imports optional; import heavy deps locally in functions if possible.
- Ensure accessibility: high-contrast toggle, informative tooltips, responsive layout.
- Provide CSV exports; PNG export optional via kaleido.
- Guard pre-emergence ET and wire to model outputs; avoid hard-coded hacks.
- Add smoke tests that import the module; skip when extras missing.
